name: fall leaves
notes:
a colorful mix of oak, birch and maple leaves for your fall or
holiday décor. use as garland, coasters or just sprinkle around
the room for that fall pop of color.
pattern uses one fall festival bundle.

experience level

* intermediate

materials

* woolstok (worsted) bundle (100% fine highland wool, 21
mini hanks: 5g/12yds each): 1 bundle (fall festival)
* size 6 (4mm) needles, or size needed to obtain gauge
* size 6 (4mm) double pointed needles, or size needed to
obtain gauge
* tapestry needle

finished measurements

* birch: 4¼" height by 3" width
* maple: 3½" height by 4½" width
* oak: 4¾" height by 3½" width

(height does not include stem)

colors shown

* fall festival bundle
